Interface VirtualServer

All Superinterfaces:
Remote
All Known Implementing Classes:
RmiClient, RmiServer, SocketServerHandler
public interface VirtualServer extends Remote
The VirtualServer interface defines the contract for a remote server in the multiplayer game environment. It provides methods for player connectivity, game management, and game mechanics, enabling interaction between clients and the server.
